Title: 012: Online Learning, Tableau Insights and Ad Hoc Analytics with Megan Putney
Description:
In this session of the Super Data Science Podcast, I chat with Up and Rising Tableau Expert Megan Putney. Learn how Megan started with Tableau through online learning, learn about Ad Hoc Analytics and gain some powerful Tableau insights.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/12
